Written by Sandeep Kewlani. Sandeep Kewlani. Sandeep Kewlani. Sandeep Kewlani. Aamil Keeyan Khan. Aamil Keeyan Khan. Aamil Keeyan Khan

Language Hindi

Production Ajay Devgn Ffilms
